@startuml
title Feature 025 - уведомления, offline, i18n и аналитика - sequence

actor "Пользователь" as User
participant "Frontend App Shell" as Shell
participant "I18nProvider" as I18n
participant "NotificationProvider" as Notification
participant "OfflineStatusProvider" as Offline
participant "AnalyticsProvider" as Analytics
participant "Auth API" as Auth
participant "platform-experience API" as Platform
participant "Yandex Metrika Adapter" as Metrika
participant "Mindbox Adapter" as Mindbox
participant "Hybrid Pixel Adapter" as Hybrid

User -> Shell: открывает маршрут платформы
Shell -> I18n: load resources_*.ts для текущей локали
Shell -> Notification: mount platform-notification-root
Shell -> Offline: subscribe browser online/offline events
Shell -> Auth: restore current session
Auth --> Shell: session context, role, route policies, active partner
Shell -> Platform: GET /runtime-config
Platform --> Shell: analytics channels, consentPolicyVersion, diagnostics flags, STR_MNEMO_PLATFORM_EXPERIENCE_CONFIG_READY
Shell -> Platform: GET /consent/preferences
Platform --> Shell: functional/analytics/marketing flags

User -> Shell: выполняет бизнес-действие
Shell -> Notification: show success/warning/error by i18n key or STR_MNEMO_*
Notification -> I18n: resolve message key/code
I18n --> Notification: localized text
Notification --> User: toast/modal без hardcoded текста
Notification -> Analytics: track NOTIFICATION_SHOWN

alt analytics consent allowed
  Analytics -> Metrika: pageview/conversion payload
  Analytics -> Mindbox: conversion payload if marketing consent allowed
  Analytics -> Hybrid: conversion payload if marketing consent allowed
else consent denied
  Analytics -> Platform: POST /diagnostics/analytics-events reason CONSENT_DENIED
end

alt adapter failed
  Metrika --> Analytics: adapter error
  Analytics -> Platform: POST /diagnostics/analytics-events status FAILED
  Analytics -> Mindbox: continue other allowed adapters
  Analytics -> Hybrid: continue other allowed adapters
end

Offline -> Shell: browser offline event
Shell -> Notification: show platform-offline-popup
Notification -> I18n: resolve offline message
Notification --> User: локализованный offline popup
Offline -> Analytics: track OFFLINE_STATE_ENTERED

Offline -> Shell: browser online event
Shell -> Auth: verify session after reconnect
Auth --> Shell: session valid
Shell -> Notification: show platform-reconnect-notification
Offline -> Analytics: track OFFLINE_STATE_RESTORED

alt missing i18n key detected
  I18n -> Platform: POST /diagnostics/i18n-missing-keys
  Platform --> I18n: STR_MNEMO_PLATFORM_DIAGNOSTIC_ACCEPTED
end

User -> Shell: tracking-admin opens /admin/analytics-diagnostics
Shell -> Platform: GET /diagnostics/summary
Platform --> Shell: channel summaries or STR_MNEMO_ANALYTICS_DIAGNOSTICS_FORBIDDEN
Shell --> User: diagnostics panel or localized forbidden state
@enduml
